label.value: basitarsal articular process of the protibia

value.value: The articular process that is located distodorsally on the protibia and bears the basitarsal fossa of the protiba.

label.value: basitarsal fossa of the metatibia

value.value: The fossa that is located on the basitarsal articular process of the metatibia and accommodates the tibial condyle of the metabasitarsus.

label.value: basitarsal articular process of the mesotibia

value.value: The articular process that is located distodorsally on the mesotibia and bears the basitarsal fossa of the protiba.

label.value: basitarsal fossa of the mesotibia

value.value: The fossa that is located on the basitarsal articular process of the mesotibia and accommodates the tibial condyle of the mesobasitarsus.

label.value: axillar phragma

value.value: The apodeme that is located submedially on the anterior part of dorsal axillar surface and corresponds to the site of origin of the anterior mesonoto-mesotrochanteral muscle.

label.value: auricle

value.value: The area that is located laterally (dorsally, externally) on the proximal margin of the metabasitarsus and accommodates the rastellum.

label.value: dilator muscle of the 6th abdominal spiracle

value.value: The spiracular muscle that arises from the lateral spiracular apodeme of the abdominal sternum 6 and inserts on the 6th abdominal spiracle.

label.value: pollen press

value.value: The anatomical cluster that is composed of the auricle and the rastellum.

label.value: articular surface

value.value: The area that is located on the sclerite and that makes movable direct contact with another sclerite.

label.value: articular membrane of the protibio-probasitarsal joint

value.value: The articular membrane that is located in the protibio-probasitarsal joint.

label.value: articular membrane of the metacoxo-metatrochanteral joint

value.value: The articular membrane that is located in the metacoxo-metatrochanteral joint.

label.value: arcus

value.value: The sclerite that encircles ventrolaterally the proximal part of the arolium.

label.value: anteroventral mesoscutal inflection

value.value: The inflection that extends along the anteroventral margin of the mesoscutum and supports the dorsal pronotal inflection.

label.value: anteromesoscutum

value.value: The area that is located anterior to the transscutal articulation.

label.value: anterolateral metapleuro-metanotal muscle

value.value: The lateral metapleuro-metanotal muscle that arises anterolaterally from the metapectus.

label.value: anterolateral metacoxo-metatrochanteral muscle

value.value: The metatrochanteral muscle that arises anteriorly from the metacoxa and inserts on the articular membrane of the metacoxo-metatrochanteral joint laterally of the anterior metacoxo-metatrochanteral articulation.

label.value: anterolateral mesopectal inflection

value.value: The inflection that extends along the anterior margin of the mesopectus and articulates with the posterior pronotal inflection.

label.value: anterior trochanteral fossa of the mesocoxa

value.value: The fossa that is located anteriorly on the distal margin of the mesocoxa accommodating the anterior coxal condyle of the mesotrochanter.

label.value: anterior trochanteral articular process of the procoxa

value.value: The articular process that is located anteriorly on the distal margin of the procoxa and bears the anterior trochanteral condyle of the procoxa.

label.value: anterior trochanteral condyle of the procoxa

value.value: The condyle that is located on the anterior trochanteral articular process of the procoxa and inserts on the anterior coxal fossa of the protrochanter.

label.value: anterior trochanteral articular process of the metacoxa

value.value: The articular process that is located anteriorly on the distal margin of the metacoxa and bears the anterior trochanteral condyle of the metacoxa.

label.value: anterior trochanteral condyle of the mesocoxa

value.value: The condyle that is located on the anterior trochanteral articular process of the mesocoxa.

label.value: anterior mesocoxo-mesotrochanteral articulation

value.value: The articulation that is composed of the anterior coxal fossa of the mesotrochanter and the anterior trochanteral condyle of the mesocoxa.

label.value: anterior coxal fossa of the protrochanter

value.value: The fossa that is located anteriorly on the proximal margin of the protrochanter accommodating the anterior trochanteral condyle of the procoxa.

label.value: anterior coxal fossa of the metatrochanter

value.value: The fossa that is located anteriorly on the metatrochanter and accommodates the anterior trochanteral condyle of the metacoxa.

label.value: anterior trochanteral condyle of the metacoxa

value.value: The condyle that is located on the anterior trochanteral articular process of the metacoxa and inserts into the anterior coxal fossa of the metacoxa.

label.value: dilator muscle of the 7th abdominal spiracle

value.value: The spiracular muscle that arises from the lateral sternal apodeme of the abdominal sternum 7 and inserts on the 7th abdominal spiracle.

label.value: dilator muscle of the 8th abdominal spiracle

value.value: The spiracular muscle that arises anteroventrally from the tergal spiracular plate and inserts on the 8th abdominal spiracle.

label.value: dilator of the propodeal spiracle muscle

value.value: The first abdominal tergal spiracle muscle that does not extend between the dorsal and ventral spiraclar apodeme but attaches to one of these apodemes.

label.value: distal fossa of the tarsomere

value.value: The fossa that is located distodorsally on the tarsomere and accommodates the proximal condyle of the subsequent tarsomere.

label.value: dorsal metapleuro-third axillary sclerite of hind wing muscle

value.value: The metapleuro-third axillary sclerite of hind wing muscle that arises dorsolaterally from the mesopleuron dorsally of the vantral metapleuro-third axillary sclerite of hind wing muscle.

label.value: syntergum

value.value: The syntergum that is the posteriormost sclerite on the dorsum of the abdomen.

label.value: episternal foveae

value.value: The row of impressions that is located on the anteroventral edge of the mesopleuron and is correspond to the site of origin of the mesopleuro-mesobasalar muscle.

label.value: epistomal line

value.value: The line that extends between the anterior tentorial pits.

label.value: femoral articular process of the mesotrochanter

value.value: The articular process that is located laterally on the distal margin of the mesotrochanter and bears the femoral condyle of the mesotrochanter.

label.value: femoral articular process of the metatrochanter

value.value: The articular process that is located laterally on the distal margin of the metatrochanter and bears the femoral condyle of the metatrochanter.

label.value: femoral articular process of the protrochanter

value.value: The articular process that is located laterally on the distal margin of the protrochanter and bears the femoral condyle of the metatrochanter.

label.value: femoral condyle of the protibia

value.value: The femoral condyle of the tibia that is located on the protibia.

label.value: femoral condyle of the tibia

value.value: The condyle that is located proximally on the tibia and inserts into the tibial fossa of the femur.

label.value: femoral fossa of the metatrochanter

value.value: The fossa that is located posteromedially on the metatrochanter and accommodates the trochanteral condyle of the metafemur.

label.value: femoro-tibial joint

value.value: The dicondylic joint that is composed of the femur and the tibia.

label.value: first mesopleuro-third axillary sclerite of fore wing muscle

value.value: The fore wing third axillary muscle that arises anterodorsally from the mesopleuron.

label.value: flexor of the pretarsal claws of the fore leg

value.value: The intrinsic leg muscle that arises from the profemoro-protibial joint and inserts on the unguitractor plate of the protarsus.

label.value: flexor of the pretarsal claws of the hind leg

value.value: The intrinsic leg muscle that arises from the metafemoro-metatibial joint and inserts on the unguitractor plate of the metatarsus.

label.value: flexor of the pretarsal claws of the middle leg

value.value: The intrinsic leg muscle that arises from the mesofemoro-mesotibial joint and inserts on the unguitractor plate of the mesotarsus.

label.value: retinaculum

value.value: The area that is located posteriorly on the fore wing, is ventrally curved and accommodate the hamuli.

label.value: frons

value.value: The area that is between the epistomal line and the anterior ocellus and limited laterally by the inner margin of compound eye.

label.value: humeral complex of the fore wing

value.value: The humeral complex that is located on the fore wing.

label.value: groove

value.value: The line that is located on the sclerite and is impressed.

label.value: genuflexor plate of the mid leg

value.value: The genuflexor plate that is located in the mid leg.
